                <h1>Discovering Windows 11 Lock Screen Wallpaper Location</h1>
                <p>Windows 11 lock screen wallpapers are stored in the following locations: C:\Windows\Web\Screen for default wallpapers and C:\Users\[Your Username]\AppData\Local\Packages\Microsoft.Windows.ShellExperienceHost_*\LocalState\Assets for personalized ones. Simply navigate to these folders to find or replace your lock screen images.</p>
